{"tid":1625351,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"迪迪尼有冇當過員工係人？","createTime":"2019-10-05T06:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:10:15.000Z","uid":65595,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8c7c7618e869871c25036aac2f2e1f1cfa208dd5","tid":1625351,"uid":65595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:39:32.000Z","msg":"今日狗鐵宣佈全線暫停服務，多間大型商場，連鎖超市都宣佈唔開，咁點解Disney仲可以一意孤行唔顧賓客及員工嘅安全繼續開park?!<br />\n<br />\n究竟所謂嘅高層有冇諗過今晚有事發生，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">得返R8巴士呢個選擇</span></strong>，咁啲同事可以點做？就算係住宿安排方面，都係以so called 尊貴嘅賓客為先，咁員工唔係人呀？<br />\n<br />\n而家最新消息，<strong>樂園有機會提早於1800/1900 close park</strong>，咁你叫啲員工咁博命仆返去返工，就係為咗做果<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五個鐘頭野</span></span>，咁有冇諗過佢哋放咗工之後嘅安全問題？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oF4Yr8W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoF4Yr8W.png&h=c368ea05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n究竟咁堅持都要開幾個鐘頭park，其實係為咩呢？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1e57d18a3edfb6ea54aacf4c346a9a7d0dff2bcd","tid":1625351,"uid":220433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b44efa450611774dec5b724d9b057d17c8327b","tid":1625351,"uid":317379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2dcdf663c123a74156b80e0c7556adf12ae25d7","tid":1625351,"uid":10450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"成班離地天堂人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee6a93d32cef383a460e59f5007cda2079faf8b","tid":1625351,"uid":11677,"like":0,"dislike":0,